    "description": "Horoscopicus is a game inspired by 2D platformers from a certain incredibly well known portable console from the 90s!<br>Play as <strong>Horo</strong> in this 2D Retro platformer and try your best to collect the 12 zodiac signs (<i>AND PET THE SECRET ANIMALS</i>) so that you may unlock the door to the mysterious 13th zodiac!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/7c97acf7047292a7c4fdd2abf29131c8.poster.avif?t=1666458692\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/7c97acf7047292a7c4fdd2abf29131c8.webm?t=1666458692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/7c97acf7047292a7c4fdd2abf29131c8.mp4?t=1666458692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/984ee8d0757236c83aac61149f45f9fd.avif?t=1666458692\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore 12 levels + Special versions, all inspired by their own unique zodiac sign!<br></li><li> Choose your own path! The initial 12 levels can be played in any order!<br></li><li> 4 Different upgrade types which change character visuals to match!<br></li><li> Find and <strong>PET 12 DIFFERENT SECRET ANIMALS!</strong> :D<br></li><li> Several selectable screen borders! (Can you find out how to change them?)<br></li><li> Lots of references to other games and media! <br></li><li> Simple controls! (A Jump button, an Attack button and directional keys for Movement.)<br></li><li> An assist/accessibility mode that can help with those particularly tough sections!<br></li><li> An amazingly unique soundtrack made by TheLuzical!<br></li><li> One difficulty, tailored to be the intended experience!<br></li><li> Speedrun friendly! (Enemies behave under cycles)<br></li><li> Total length of the game should be around 3h~, though it highly depends from player to player! :)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/88176acc40fd981cbadb52df3c971c15.avif?t=1666458692\" width=600 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimer:</h2>This is my first big game and it was completed <i>mostly</i> as a solo project.<br>While I got some help during development, expect a more &quot;traditional indie&quot; quality to the game! :)<br>Nonetheless, I hope you manage to enjoy it regardless!",
